{"tid":1578391,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【反思／政治哲學】","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:07:27.000Z","uid":94227,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd9e19c8e2b14106e6e5d1ffa77444306efb3d7","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"有見大部分公民講堂都缺乏政治哲學既元素 所以一直幾想打篇政治哲學既野 為成個運動既前因後果、抗爭形式、以至其本質提供一個justification 同解釋<br />\n<br />\n但一黎小弟不才 驚有錯處同唔夠solid<br />\n二黎揾唔岩時機 係大家情緒高漲既時候企係高處分析 只怕大家亦可能聽唔入耳<br />\n<br />\n而哲學有偈傾十分有心 幫我同大家做左一個簡短既分析同討論 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>希望和理非同勇武都可抽小小時間睇左佢</strong></span> 甚至推比對家睇下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw5npso82pKs&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=fa976523\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs</a><br />\n<br />\n內容由和理非、勇武既moral justification 以至just war（禍必及妻兒？）既討論都有 中間穿插其他議題 例如法治 但仍有唔少可補充之處 歡迎大家討論"},{"pid":"5d0e339c05457d3f4c8d0da73c470afc5961a310","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"自推 一"},{"pid":"bb32dfd088e50c3fc43e95cf559b543662fa3489","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"自推 二"},{"pid":"85e438eef0e5f136ec3f82bef250fa3625acf187","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"自推 三"},{"pid":"ab16c3c114a1b3acbec092bdd4db2c4c7d5e8fd0","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"自推 四"},{"pid":"9eaefee74d4b8198bd5419cfe533b785446b040c","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"自推 五"},{"pid":"511ded6833edf291c951025832caada6fc4e54c4","tid":1578391,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-1